{"tid":768964,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖）到底邊個最柒？","createTime":"2018-08-05T23:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T00:28:51.000Z","uid":167326,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0f8d6d9580276d644bce19164aaba0f883d740","tid":768964,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T23:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/074725_632546d116f65eac5b95f8711f8e875d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F074725_632546d116f65eac5b95f8711f8e875d.png&h=ec3f12e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/074726_632546d116f65eac5b95f8711f8e875d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F074726_632546d116f65eac5b95f8711f8e875d.png&h=0f76a544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我只係路過 食花生<br />\n見到IG個廣告講咩招啲有才華嘅人訓練<br />\n但只見到個黑妹係度咪嘴<br />\n好奇睇下啲留言點睇件事啦<br />\n點知見到3隻小學雞係度嘈 邊個柒<br />\n成埋留言157個 佢地嘈左85個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n內容大致討論 <br />\n到底 唔知咪嘴係乜野留言問個fd柒D?<br />\n定係 屌鳩個小學雞搭嗲柒D<br />\n還是 無啦啦懶醒走去搭嗲屌鳩人唔識咪嘴柒D?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我都只不過好心<br />\n見佢地3個討論唔出結果 <br />\n就幫佢地問下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f4117cfcebddf5b9398106462c9d50b5d6f126","tid":768964,"uid":24534,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:03:13.000Z","msg":"乜鳩都post上黎最柒"},{"pid":"a3d530dbb4abd091ced5d4329ff5898c09a49d5d","tid":768964,"uid":33004,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:04:49.000Z","msg":"樓豬最柒"},{"pid":"582aafbee2c3ac946bc8ffd85c7aa804c871bc7a","tid":768964,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:08:24.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"7c80f76c453b155a0d57ca8c034b863c1009697b"